## 🏗️ Kiến trúc ứng dụng

### Mô hình: MVVM + Repository Pattern

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│              UI Layer                    │
│  (Jetpack Compose Screens/Components)   │
│         ↕ State (StateFlow)             │
│           ViewModel Layer               │
│         ↕ Data operations               │
│          Repository Layer               │
│         ↕ Firebase SDK                  │
│            Data Layer                   │
│  (Firebase Auth / Firestore / FCM)      │
└─────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Cấu trúc package

```
com.hotelbooking.app/
├── data/
│   ├── model/          → Data classes: Hotel, User, Booking, Room, Message
│   ├── repository/     → HotelRepository, BookingRepository, ChatRepository, AuthRepository
│   └── remote/         → FirebaseAuthService, FirestoreService, FCMService
├── di/                 → AppModule.kt, RepositoryModule.kt (Hilt)
├── ui/
│   ├── theme/          → Color.kt, Type.kt, Shape.kt, Theme.kt
│   ├── components/     → HotelCard, SearchBar, BookingCard, RatingStars, ...
│   ├── navigation/     → NavGraph.kt, Routes.kt
│   └── screens/
│       ├── auth/       → LoginScreen, RegisterScreen, AuthViewModel
│       ├── home/       → HomeScreen, HomeViewModel
│       ├── detail/     → HotelDetailScreen, HotelDetailViewModel
│       ├── booking/    → BookingScreen, BookingViewModel, MyBookingsScreen
│       ├── chat/       → ChatScreen, ChatViewModel, ChatListScreen
│       ├── profile/    → ProfileScreen, ProfileViewModel
│       └── manager/    → ManagerDashboard, AddHotelScreen, ManageRoomsScreen
├── util/               → Constants.kt, Extensions.kt, DateUtils.kt
├── service/            → FCMNotificationService.kt
└── HotelBookingApp.kt  → @HiltAndroidApp Application class
```

---

## 🗃️ Cấu trúc Firestore Database

### Collections

```
users/
  └── {userId}/
      ├── email: String
      ├── displayName: String
      ├── role: String ("customer" | "manager")
      ├── phoneNumber: String
      ├── avatarUrl: String
      └── createdAt: Timestamp

hotels/
  └── {hotelId}/
      ├── name: String
      ├── description: String
      ├── address: String
      ├── city: String
      ├── rating: Double
      ├── imageUrls: List<String>
      ├── amenities: List<String>
      ├── priceRange: Map {min, max}
      ├── managerId: String (ref → users)
      ├── createdAt: Timestamp
      └── rooms/ (subcollection)
          └── {roomId}/
              ├── type: String
              ├── price: Double
              ├── capacity: Int
              ├── isAvailable: Boolean
              └── imageUrl: String

bookings/
  └── {bookingId}/
      ├── userId: String (ref → users)
      ├── hotelId: String (ref → hotels)
      ├── roomId: String (ref → rooms)
      ├── checkIn: Timestamp
      ├── checkOut: Timestamp
      ├── totalPrice: Double
      ├── status: String ("pending" | "confirmed" | "cancelled" | "completed")
      ├── guestCount: Int
      └── createdAt: Timestamp

messages/
  └── {chatId}/
      ├── participants: List<String> [userId, managerId]
      ├── lastMessage: String
      ├── lastMessageAt: Timestamp
      └── messages/ (subcollection)
          └── {messageId}/
              ├── senderId: String
              ├── text: String
              ├── timestamp: Timestamp
              └── isRead: Boolean
```

